{
  "stem": "19502.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She couldn't speak a word Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After 20 years in the country, she couldn't speak Polish but only Russian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she was very, very pleased.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, it was her language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Secondly, she was-- she'll be able to get in touch with her family because her family-- she left her family in Russia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So after a while, I mean, things started to go to normal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went to school, and education was A-1.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They demanded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was-- then they made us from children pioneers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were pioneers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They put us on with the red scarves and with-- with-- with-- with the little emblem in here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And who says you can't brainwash.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Father Stalin-- I came home, I says he's the Father Stalin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He's our liberator.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He's-- he's nothing but the best.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And next-- and God wasn't supposed to be mentioned, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Then-- but we went to school five days a week, no six days a week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You see we went-- we went to school on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No-- no Sunday we didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had to go to school on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we had to write on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So to some people was very, very hard to get used to the idea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But when they went to the Talbut, I mean, not to-- but to the-- to the Jewish school, they had went on Sunday and didn't go Saturday.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So this was all right for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- when Russia invaded our town, I was 12, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was finished grade six, no?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went into grade seven to the Russian, you know, when the Russian came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, I found it easy because my mother spoke and I knew the language.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
